high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the table, turn to the right to face the couch.
Pick up the set of keys that is on the couch.
Turn to the right, go forward to the table on the right where the cardboard box is.
Put the keys inside the cardboard box that is on the table.
Pick up the cardboard box from the table.
Turn to the right, go forward, hang a left, turn around to face the couch.
Put the cardboard box down on the center cushion of the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box containing keys on a couch.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the left side of the couch on your right and then turn right to face it when you get there.
Pick up the keys that are in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the side of the coffee table on your right turning right to face it when you get there.
Put the keys in the box on the coffee table.
Pick up the box with the keys in it.
Turn around and take a step to your left then take a step back.
Put the box on the couch where the cushion all the way to the left meets the middle cushion near the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with keys in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, move forward toward the end of the couch, then turn right.
Pick up the keys from the couch.
Turn right, move forward, then turn right to face the coffee table.
Put the keys in the box on the coffee table.
Pick up the box from the coffee table.
Turn right, move forward, turn left, then turn around to face the couch.
Put the box on the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with keys in it on the couch.
